dip.gui

Class ClientMenu

  • java.lang.Object
    • dip.gui.ClientMenu

  • public class ClientMenu
extends java.lang.Object
    Implements many menu methods, and constructs the menus.

    This is fully internationlizable (il8n) via the il8n.properties file
